Assume SERVEROUTPUT is ON. Given table q19_products with the columns product_id, product_name, price. It contains exactly one row with product_id=5, product_name='Mouse', and price=80.

What will this block display?

Code:
DECLARE
  r q19_products%ROWTYPE;
BEGIN
  SELECT * INTO r
  FROM q19_products
  WHERE product_id = 5;

  r.price := r.price + 20;

  UPDATE q19_products
  SET price = r.price
  WHERE product_id = r.product_id;

  DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(r.product_name || ':' || SQL%ROWCOUNT || ':' || r.price);
END;
/

